        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Denying Firearms and Explosives to Dangerous Terrorists Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Justice to deny the transfer of firearms and explosives or the issuance of related licenses to a known or suspected terrorist. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
